---------vim editor commends-----------------------
vim <fname> used for  file open on vim
esc+i got insert mode
gg -beging of file
G - last line or ground line of file
yy -copy a line
nyy -
p -past
u -undo
dd- delecte aline
ndd -delete a n lines
dw delete a word
ndw
x -cut a charector
:set num used for set numbers on editer
:set nonu
:wq used for save and quit


